    • Method Detail

      • detect

        public static int detect​(java.lang.String fullName)
                  throws java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException

        Analyzes the naming pattern of the name to detect its gender.

        Obs.: This function only works in "Brazilian Portuguese" names.

        Parameters:
        fullName - Full name to analyze. Surname will be ignored automatically.
        Returns:
        [-1] - Invalid
        [ 0] - Undefined
        [ 1] - Feminine
        [ 2] - Masculine
        Throws:
        java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException - If the algorithm tries to access an invalid position in the name.
